📁 Files to Create / Modify
───────────────────────────────────────────────────

New:
- SwiftLoginScreen/Alerts/AlertPresenter.swift
    - UIViewController extension (presentAlert, presentAlertWithFunction removed)
    - AlertItem struct
    - AlertAction enum

Modified:
- SwiftLoginScreen/HomeVC.swift
    - Remove UIViewController extension (move to AlertPresenter.swift)

- SwiftLoginScreen/MenuVC.swift
    - Update presentAlertWithFunction call → presentAlert(action: .resendActivation)

- SwiftLoginScreen/BroadCasting/Websocket.swift
    - Add PassthroughSubject<WebSocketMessage, Never>
    - Add WebSocketMessage enum
    - Add SeatUpdate model
    - Replace print() in receiveMessage() with subject.send(parsed)

- SwiftLoginScreen/SeatsVC.swift (or SeatMapViewModel if already extracted)
    - Subscribe to WebSocketManager.messagePublisher
    - On seatUpdate matching current screeningDateId: refresh seat list
    - Show inline "Seat map updated" indicator (not modal alert)
    - On genericNotification: presentAlert

- SwiftLoginScreen/AppServices.swift (or AppDelegate.swift)
    - Ensure WebSocketManager instance is accessible via HasAppServices

