📊 Success Criteria
───────────────────────────────────────────────────

Alerts:
- [ ] AlertPresenter.swift exists; UIViewController extension is NOT in HomeVC.swift
- [ ] All 20 existing presentAlert call sites compile unchanged
- [ ] MenuVC resendActivation path uses AlertAction.resendActivation (no magic string)
- [ ] AlertItem can be used in any SwiftUI view with .alert(item:)
- [ ] No UIAlertView usage exists anywhere in the codebase

WebSocket:
- [ ] WebSocketManager publishes typed WebSocketMessage (not just print)
- [ ] SeatsVC refreshes seat map on receiving seatUpdate for current screeningDateId
- [ ] No modal alert interrupts seat selection for seatUpdate events
- [ ] genericNotification shows a modal alert
- [ ] Reconnect behavior is unchanged
- [ ] Existing ping/pong timer is unaffected

General:
- [ ] No regression in BasketVC checkout, MenuVC logout, PurchasesVC delete,
      SignupVC flows
- [ ] No new third-party dependencies introduced

